        public KBData(KBData that)

    • Method Detail

      • lock

        public static byte[] lock(File pdfFile)
        Returns a byte array suitable for use as the PDF password based on the dbID/parentDirectory name of the given file. If the parent directory is NOT an 18 character KnowledgeBin ID it returns null
        Parameters:
        pdfFile - The file to encrypt
        Returns:
        a byte array suitable for use as the PDF password based on the dbID/parentDirectory name of the given file, or null.

      • lock

        Parameters:
        req - ignored argument for obscuration
        Returns:
        a byte array suitable for use as the PDF password based on the dbID/parentDirectory name of the current URL.
